    Note: 1. Pure function call elimination - remove calls to pure functions if result unused
    Let pure_functions be proc memory_get_int64 from Layout with wpa, 72
    Let eliminated_pure_calls be eliminate_unused_pure_calls(mir, pure_functions)

    Note: 2. Const function memoization - cache results of const functions
    Let const_functions be proc memory_get_int64 from Layout with wpa, 80
    Let memoized_calls be memoize_const_function_calls(mir, const_functions)

