    Note: Verify value dominance properties
    Note: For each use of a value, verify the definition dominates the use
    Note: This requires dominance tree computation - skipped for basic verification
    Note: Full verification would build dominance tree and check dominance property

    Note: All basic checks passed
    Return 1
