    Note: receives 0 and the verification failure propagates through the
    Note: orchestrator's hard-failure path instead of being silently
    Note: "repaired". A genuine snapshot/restore facility requires a deep
    Note: MIR copy taken BEFORE Phase B and belongs to the optimizer
    Note: driver that owns the MIR arena, not to this struct.
