@Reasoning
apply_constant_propagation_candidate applies a single constant propagation
identified by index into wpa.constant_prop_candidates.

Bucket 0x0007 dispatches here. The candidate format is the 24-byte CP
candidate struct from design section 7: value_id(0), constant_value(8),
context_function(16). Replaces all uses of value_id in context_function
with constant_value.
