by index into wpa.specialization_candidates.

Bucket 0x0008 dispatches here. The candidate format is the 32-byte
SpecCandidate struct from design section 7: callee_id(0),
const_args_pattern(8), call_frequency(16), benefit_score(24). Creates a
specialized clone of callee_id parameterized on const_args_pattern.
